sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant PI as Pi runtime
    participant EXT as Extension
    participant FS as ~/.pi/evolver/
    participant DAE as daemon.mjs

    U->>PI: start session
    PI->>EXT: session_start
    EXT->>FS: init in-memory stats

    PI->>EXT: before_agent_start
    EXT->>FS: read digest.md
    EXT-->>PI: inject digest into system prompt

    loop each turn
        PI->>EXT: tool_execution_start
        PI->>EXT: tool_result
        EXT->>EXT: count calls, hash errors
    end

    U->>PI: exit
    PI->>EXT: session_shutdown
    EXT->>FS: append event to events.jsonl
    EXT->>FS: append line to evolver.log

    Note over DAE,FS: launchd fires every 6 h
    DAE->>FS: read last 500 events
    DAE->>DAE: analyze streaks, saturation, errsigs
    DAE->>FS: rewrite digest.md and digest.json
    DAE->>FS: updatePersonality clamped
    DAE->>FS: append line to evolver.log